Sentencas: This work reports on the testing of a 100-W intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell stack (IT-SOFC).
Titulo: Experimental Activity on a 100-W IT-SOFC Test Bench Fed by Simulated Syngas

Sentencas: The stack was tested both in feeding conditions with pure hydrogen and with syngas.
Titulo: Experimental Activity on a 100-W IT-SOFC Test Bench Fed by Simulated Syngas

Sentencas: In the latter case, different types of feeding gas mixtures were considered that differ from each other in the composition of their gaseous substances and the quantity of CO in the mixtures.
Titulo: Experimental Activity on a 100-W IT-SOFC Test Bench Fed by Simulated Syngas

Sentencas: For cases of stack feeding with mixtures containing carbon monoxide, the influence of the reformer temperature on the output obtained was also evaluated.
Titulo: Experimental Activity on a 100-W IT-SOFC Test Bench Fed by Simulated Syngas

Sentencas: The stack operation was tested by changing some operating conditions such as the temperature of the SOFC stack and the fuel use factor.
Titulo: Experimental Activity on a 100-W IT-SOFC Test Bench Fed by Simulated Syngas

Sentencas: The polarization curves of the stack were obtained in order to vary the operating conditions.
Titulo: Experimental Activity on a 100-W IT-SOFC Test Bench Fed by Simulated Syngas

Sentencas: Furthermore, mapping of the stack performances in terms of electric efficiency and power produced was carried out.
Titulo: Experimental Activity on a 100-W IT-SOFC Test Bench Fed by Simulated Syngas
